+ (NSString*)cacheIpsum
{
    return @"We love having members of the geocaching community come and visit us in our awesome lobby! We kindly ask that you do not just drop in but rather, please email to schedule your visit in advance via hqvisits@geocaching.com. Tell us the date you'd like to visit, how many cachers (or muggles) to expect and their respective geocaching usernames, where you're visiting us from and any other fun facts about you.\n\n"
    
    @"Historically, geocachers were able to log the HQ cache only on Fridays! You are now able to log the cache Tuesday through Friday by appointment, typically scheduled in the afternoons. We kindly request that you email to schedule your visit to ensure we have enough space to accommodate all our visitors and are in fact open.\n\n";
}

